item.title: Divine-Reality || Oldschool || Economy || Iron Man || Boss Minipets || New OSRS
item.dc:creator: @wheresmydrop wheresmydrop
item.description:
@wheresmydrop wrote:

Soulcist:

That achievement diary interface is really nice, I love it. Other than that, I see some potential for the server and hope it’s doing well (as I assume this isn’t a new one from the looks of it, and the forums). Also, the forum themselves… perhaps find someone to make a custom theme or something, the current one is overused. And those crowns looks awful.

The purpose of the server is for the game-play, the forum style is used because it’s dark and easy on the eyes. For the crowns I guess you can’t make everyone happy. Thanks for the feedback.

On another note Tim is continuing to bring us weekly patches and updates, listening to all suggestions proposed on the forums. It has been a good month for DR.

Read full topic
